        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iovi Optimo <lb n="2"/>Maximo Iuno<lb break="no" n="3"/>ni Reginae Min<lb break="no" n="4"/>ervae sanctae <lb n="5"/>Soli Mithrae <lb n="6"/>Herculi Mar<lb break="no" n="7"/>ti Mercurio <lb n="8"/>Genio loci di<lb break="no" n="9"/>is deabusque <lb n="10"/>omnibus M<lb break="no" n="11"/>arcus Aureli<lb break="no" n="12"/>us Decimus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>raeses</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rovinciae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>N</abbr><ex>umidiae</ex></expan> ex principe pe<lb break="no" n="14"/>regrinorum <lb n="15"/>votum solvit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: M. Aurelius Decimus war 284 n. Chr. Statthalter in Numidien.</p>
            </div>
